<%- include("partials/header") %>

<section class="legend-page legend-trickster">
  <div class="container legend-shell">
    <div class="legend-grid">
      <div class="legend-poster-wrap trickster-glow">
        <div class="legend-poster">
          <div class="legend-coming-soon">Coming Soon</div>
          <div class="legend-placeholder">
            <div class="legend-placeholder-box">
              <div class="legend-placeholder-text">Loki Image Placeholder</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="legend-copy">
        <div class="legend-badges">
          <span class="legend-badge trickster">Trickster</span>
          <span class="legend-tier">Mythic</span>
        </div>

        <h1>Loki</h1>
        <p class="legend-role">God of Mischief</p>
        <p class="legend-lead">
          Loki is deception, intelligence, and beautiful danger hiding behind a smile.
        </p>

        <div class="legend-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/">Return Home</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/characters/donner">View Donner</a>
        </div>

        <div class="legend-panels">
          <div class="legend-panel">
            <h2>Description</h2>
            <p>
              Loki bends trust until it breaks. He is not dangerous only because he lies,
              but because he understands exactly what people want to believe. In war, he
              weaponizes uncertainty, motive, and perception. A blade may cut flesh, but
              Loki cuts alliances, confidence, and peace of mind.
            </p>

            <div class="legend-power-grid">
              <div class="legend-power-card"><h3>Illusion Craft</h3><p>Twists sight, truth, and perception.</p></div>
              <div class="legend-power-card"><h3>Strategic Manipulation</h3><p>Turns trust into a battlefield weakness.</p></div>
              <div class="legend-power-card"><h3>Verbal Precision</h3><p>Provokes, seduces, and divides with words.</p></div>
              <div class="legend-power-card"><h3>Chaos Intelligence</h3><p>Thrives where others lose control.</p></div>
            </div>

            <div class="legend-quote">“The deadliest traps are the ones people call truth.”</div>
          </div>

          <div class="legend-panel">
            <h2>Profile</h2>
            <div class="legend-profile">
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Faction</span><span class="legend-value">Asgard</span></div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Role</span><span class="legend-value">God of Mischief</span></div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Power Theme</span><span class="legend-value">Illusion / Manipulation / Cunning</span></div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Visual</span><span class="legend-value">Image Coming Soon</span></div>
              <div class="legend-row"><span class="legend-label">Background</span><span class="legend-value">Placeholder Active</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

